1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:03,520
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:03,520 --> 00:00:06,110
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:06,780 --> 00:00:10,180
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:14,890
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:15,260 --> 00:00:17,790
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:18,130 --> 00:00:21,570
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:28,540
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:29,220 --> 00:00:34,300
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:37,590
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:37,590 --> 00:00:40,200
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:47,980
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:00:48,950 --> 00:00:51,710
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:54,610
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:55,930
♪Let me♪

15
00:00:56,120 --> 00:01:00,200
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:00,650 --> 00:01:03,330
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:06,320
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:06,490 --> 00:01:07,960
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:12,130
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:12,490 --> 00:01:22,740
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:24,170 --> 00:01:29,720
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:32,860
=Episode 27=

23
00:01:33,910 --> 00:01:35,390
By wearing that mask this time,

24
00:01:36,430 --> 00:01:38,390
you've terrified the Wutuo forces.

25
00:01:39,030 --> 00:01:40,470
He Rufei will certainly use this

26
00:01:40,910 --> 00:01:42,190
to confirm your identity.

27
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:46,150
Since I've come to Rundu,

28
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:47,870
I'm not afraid of him knowing.

29
00:01:49,030 --> 00:01:49,950
When I return,

30
00:01:50,870 --> 00:01:53,630
I'll stand before him
with my head held high.

31
00:01:54,670 --> 00:01:55,750
I'll make sure he learns

32
00:01:57,910 --> 00:02:00,790
who the real General Feihong is.

33
00:02:04,110 --> 00:02:04,950
Speaking of which,

34
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,750
since He Rufei and Xu Jingfu

35
00:02:07,910 --> 00:02:09,190
have been colluding for so long,

36
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:10,550
there must be evidence

37
00:02:10,949 --> 00:02:12,270
of their collaboration.

38
00:02:12,870 --> 00:02:13,750
And that evidence

39
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:15,030
is in the capital.

40
00:02:15,630 --> 00:02:16,990
That's why I want to return sooner

41
00:02:17,230 --> 00:02:19,150
to investigate potential leads.

42
00:02:20,190 --> 00:02:21,030
Alright.

43
00:02:21,390 --> 00:02:22,270
I'll go with you.

44
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,150
Young Master.

45
00:02:35,070 --> 00:02:35,910
What happened to you?

46
00:02:44,230 --> 00:02:47,230
I thought you sent Miss He
medicine to restore her energy.

47
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,030
Yingxiang.

48
00:03:08,070 --> 00:03:08,910
Tell me,

49
00:03:10,430 --> 00:03:12,150
why do people yearn for light?

50
00:03:13,830 --> 00:03:14,790
Because of its warmth.

51
00:03:16,630 --> 00:03:17,470
But Young Master,

52
00:03:18,430 --> 00:03:19,870
not everyone needs it.

53
00:03:29,829 --> 00:03:30,670
Aren't you afraid

54
00:03:30,870 --> 00:03:31,710
of fire anymore?

55
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:36,470
I received warmth.

56
00:03:36,910 --> 00:03:38,270
So the fear vanished.

57
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:42,230
Is it because of Miss He?

58
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:04,110
Temporary gains and losses mean little.

59
00:04:04,750 --> 00:04:06,390
I've been maneuvering against Master

60
00:04:06,750 --> 00:04:09,790
for so long to gain power and strength

61
00:04:10,990 --> 00:04:12,390
to protect what I value.

62
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:14,350
Even so,

63
00:04:14,690 --> 00:04:16,630
you shouldn't have risked your life

64
00:04:17,589 --> 00:04:19,190
and come to such a dangerous place.

65
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:22,110
You barely dispelled
Chancellor Xu's suspicions.

66
00:04:22,390 --> 00:04:23,670
Then you came here recklessly.

67
00:04:24,430 --> 00:04:26,230
Chancellor Xu may hold it against you.

68
00:04:27,230 --> 00:04:28,310
It is dangerous here,

69
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:30,790
but an official can't

70
00:04:31,350 --> 00:04:32,590
prioritize personal safety.

71
00:04:32,950 --> 00:04:34,870
I'm obligated to come here.

72
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:38,070
And my decision proves to be right.

73
00:04:39,070 --> 00:04:40,190
I defended Rundu

74
00:04:40,830 --> 00:04:42,110
and protected its people.

75
00:04:42,950 --> 00:04:44,190
And after this battle,

76
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:46,230
His Majesty will trust me more.

77
00:04:47,190 --> 00:04:48,270
Also, I came here

78
00:04:49,230 --> 00:04:50,630
to verify something.

79
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:52,870
What is it?

80
00:04:54,390 --> 00:04:55,230
Yingxiang.

81
00:04:55,670 --> 00:04:56,510
How do you think

82
00:04:57,030 --> 00:04:59,390
General Feihong
before the Mingshui Battle

83
00:04:59,750 --> 00:05:01,230
is different from

84
00:05:01,550 --> 00:05:02,390
the current one?

85
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,510
The former General Feihong

86
00:05:05,790 --> 00:05:07,830
was valiant and strategically brilliant.

87
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,270
The current one,

88
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:12,790
as seen in the recent Huayuan Battle,

89
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:14,550
won the battle

90
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:16,990
by sacrificing seven warriors at once.

91
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:18,670
This hardly matches

92
00:05:18,870 --> 00:05:19,870
his reputation.

93
00:05:21,110 --> 00:05:22,310
And in the Rundu Battle,

94
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,070
though General Feihong

95
00:05:24,230 --> 00:05:26,230
is said to treat his troops like family,

96
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:28,830
he completely ignored

97
00:05:29,590 --> 00:05:31,230
Li Kuang's pleas for reinforcement.

98
00:05:32,470 --> 00:05:34,510
This is nothing like what we've heard.

99
00:05:35,710 --> 00:05:36,590
On the contrary,

100
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,350
back in Jiyang,

101
00:05:38,950 --> 00:05:40,070
He Yan reacted weirdly

102
00:05:40,150 --> 00:05:41,390
when she heard that He Rufei

103
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:42,790
made Chai Anxi withhold

104
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,510
Xiao Zhongwu's plea for help.

105
00:05:45,470 --> 00:05:47,110
And after she heard that seven out of

106
00:05:47,190 --> 00:05:48,510
the Eight Warriors died,

107
00:05:49,070 --> 00:05:50,630
she wielded her whip all night.

108
00:05:51,150 --> 00:05:53,030
Only deep bonds could cause

109
00:05:53,470 --> 00:05:54,390
such a reaction.

110
00:05:54,870 --> 00:05:57,350
She then rushed to Rundu overnight
to help Li Kuang

111
00:05:57,630 --> 00:05:58,790
defend the city.

112
00:05:59,590 --> 00:06:00,430
And Li Kuang

113
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:03,110
is one of He Rufei's Eight Warriors.

114
00:06:03,710 --> 00:06:05,350
Connecting the dots,

115
00:06:05,750 --> 00:06:07,070
the coincidences pile up.

116
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:11,270
Are you suggesting

117
00:06:12,150 --> 00:06:14,630
the current General Feihong
is an impostor

118
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:16,230
and Miss He is...?

119
00:06:16,230 --> 00:06:17,070
That's right.

120
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:21,150
That's my second reason for coming here.

121
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:22,630
Only in Rundu

122
00:06:22,910 --> 00:06:24,270
can I unravel these doubts.

123
00:06:24,910 --> 00:06:26,030
And it's proven

124
00:06:26,150 --> 00:06:27,110
that I'm right.

125
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:28,910
She knows about

126
00:06:28,910 --> 00:06:30,190
the secret tunnel,

127
00:06:30,790 --> 00:06:32,630
masters He Rufei's martial skills.

128
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:34,350
and even impersonates

129
00:06:34,550 --> 00:06:35,950
General Feihong perfectly.

130
00:06:36,470 --> 00:06:38,670
All these clues point to her,

131
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:40,470
proving

132
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:42,710
that she

133
00:06:43,150 --> 00:06:45,430
is the true General Feihong.

134
00:06:46,390 --> 00:06:47,230
Young Master.

135
00:06:47,350 --> 00:06:48,550
You can report this

136
00:06:48,710 --> 00:06:50,510
to Chancellor Xu once we return.

137
00:06:51,070 --> 00:06:52,790
Tell him that you came

138
00:06:52,990 --> 00:06:53,870
to investigate.

139
00:06:54,470 --> 00:06:55,510
In that case,

140
00:06:56,550 --> 00:06:57,790
he won't blame you

141
00:06:57,870 --> 00:06:59,270
for coming here without permission.

142
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:01,630
From Chai Anxi's account,

143
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:04,070
Master had contacted
the current He Rufei

144
00:07:04,230 --> 00:07:06,350
even before the Mingshui Battle.

145
00:07:08,070 --> 00:07:10,230
This isn't merely He Rufei's secret.

146
00:07:10,550 --> 00:07:12,150
It's also Master's secret.

147
00:07:13,110 --> 00:07:14,390
Given his trust issue,

148
00:07:14,870 --> 00:07:16,070
I can't tell him that

149
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:18,110
I've learned his secrets.

150
00:07:19,030 --> 00:07:20,150
So how will you

151
00:07:20,790 --> 00:07:22,510
explain it to Chancellor Xu?

152
00:07:22,790 --> 00:07:24,510
He Rufei has caused so much trouble.

153
00:07:24,870 --> 00:07:25,990
Xiao Jue and He Yan

154
00:07:26,110 --> 00:07:27,350
won't let this go easily.

155
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:29,190
He Rufei is in deep trouble.

156
00:07:29,470 --> 00:07:30,950
Master lacks capable aides.

157
00:07:31,190 --> 00:07:32,110
He'll need me.

158
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,310
And his past misdeeds

159
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:35,870
will inevitably surface.

160
00:07:36,390 --> 00:07:37,909
He'll reap what he's sown.

161
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:40,990
Though a mentor is to be

162
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,350
revered as a father,

163
00:07:43,350 --> 00:07:44,870
when it comes to Wei,

164
00:07:45,750 --> 00:07:46,950
I have my principles.

165
00:07:47,790 --> 00:07:49,150
I can't feign ignorance

166
00:07:49,909 --> 00:07:50,950
of his treason

167
00:07:52,190 --> 00:07:53,950
just because he's my master.

168
00:07:56,670 --> 00:07:57,510
Yingxiang.

169
00:07:58,030 --> 00:07:58,870
Make preparations.

170
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,590
We'll head back tomorrow.

171
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:01,870
Understood.

172
00:08:11,150 --> 00:08:12,590
Mr. He, Commander Xiao.

173
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:15,790
Mr. Chu.

174
00:08:20,870 --> 00:08:22,390
I'm heading back today

175
00:08:22,670 --> 00:08:23,870
and came to say goodbye.

176
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,110
Today?

177
00:08:27,790 --> 00:08:28,830
We will return soon.

178
00:08:29,390 --> 00:08:31,350
Won't you join us
to look after each other?

179
00:08:33,789 --> 00:08:34,710
To be honest,

180
00:08:35,270 --> 00:08:36,190
I came here

181
00:08:36,429 --> 00:08:37,630
without Master's permission.

182
00:08:38,830 --> 00:08:40,429
So I must return earlier

183
00:08:40,710 --> 00:08:41,630
to ask for forgiveness.

184
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:44,830
Mr. Chu.

185
00:08:45,270 --> 00:08:46,110
Take a seat.

186
00:08:52,070 --> 00:08:52,910
Mr. Chu.

187
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:55,590
About what happened
in Jiyang, Huayuan, and Rundu,

188
00:08:55,990 --> 00:08:57,630
have you suspected

189
00:08:58,110 --> 00:08:59,190
that these battles

190
00:08:59,670 --> 00:09:00,670
weren't coincidental?

191
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:04,150
These battles were indeed suspicious.

192
00:09:04,790 --> 00:09:05,750
Back in Jiyang,

193
00:09:06,270 --> 00:09:08,910
we found Wutuo spies in the city.

194
00:09:09,750 --> 00:09:11,110
As for Huayuan and Rundu,

195
00:09:12,190 --> 00:09:13,030
Wutuo forces

196
00:09:13,630 --> 00:09:16,550
couldn't have besieged them
so effortlessly without informants.

197
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,150
Rundu especially.

198
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:19,950
Commander Li mentioned

199
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:21,790
that the city's defenses

200
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:24,630
were utterly useless during the siege.

201
00:09:25,310 --> 00:09:26,150
It proves that

202
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:27,630
the enemies

203
00:09:27,630 --> 00:09:30,070
obtained Rundu's defense layouts
long beforehand.

204
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:32,510
Mr. Chu.

205
00:09:32,950 --> 00:09:33,790
As smart as you are,

206
00:09:34,510 --> 00:09:36,190
you must have realized

207
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,390
that all the traces

208
00:09:37,830 --> 00:09:39,470
point to one person.

209
00:09:40,430 --> 00:09:41,430
Yet even so,

210
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:44,990
won't you rein in your path?

211
00:09:48,990 --> 00:09:50,150
Everything points

212
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,710
directly to my master.

213
00:09:53,710 --> 00:09:55,070
But these are speculations.

214
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,590
Even with Chai Anxi's testimony,

215
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:58,590
there's no proof.

216
00:09:59,030 --> 00:10:00,350
I owe everything to my master.

217
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:02,550
I can't sever my ties with him
until I find

218
00:10:02,790 --> 00:10:03,630
solid evidence.

219
00:10:04,910 --> 00:10:06,030
Even if there is evidence,

220
00:10:07,150 --> 00:10:07,990
you wouldn't

221
00:10:08,270 --> 00:10:09,910
forsake your master, would you?

222
00:10:10,190 --> 00:10:12,070
After all, you learned the way

223
00:10:12,430 --> 00:10:14,070
of doing things from him.

224
00:10:17,710 --> 00:10:18,710
Please elaborate.

225
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:20,670
After the Battle of Que City,

226
00:10:21,070 --> 00:10:23,110
all sorts of rumors ran rampant.

227
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:24,350
Our investigation

228
00:10:24,750 --> 00:10:26,270
suggested it was your doing.

229
00:10:27,670 --> 00:10:28,510
In Yezhou,

230
00:10:28,910 --> 00:10:30,270
Feinu fought a masked woman

231
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:32,150
while retrieving the tax ledgers.

232
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:33,630
Her physique

233
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,670
and mannerisms

234
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:39,590
closely resembled your maid.

235
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:43,270
Coincidentally,

236
00:10:44,230 --> 00:10:45,630
that same maid was absent

237
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:47,670
from your side at the time.

238
00:10:49,150 --> 00:10:51,190
Later, Sun Xiangfu was assassinated.

239
00:10:52,670 --> 00:10:53,510
All these events

240
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:55,590
seem

241
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:58,270
connected to you.

242
00:10:58,870 --> 00:10:59,710
Commander Xiao,

243
00:11:00,470 --> 00:11:03,150
you yourself used the word "seem".

244
00:11:04,230 --> 00:11:06,670
Baseless claims aren't worth mentioning.

245
00:11:08,830 --> 00:11:09,670
However,

246
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:11,510
I've found something else

247
00:11:12,390 --> 00:11:13,950
rather intriguing.

248
00:11:14,670 --> 00:11:16,910
While investigating
the assassins who killed Chai Anxi

249
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:18,550
in Jiyang,

250
00:11:19,590 --> 00:11:21,390
someone secretly helped us,

251
00:11:22,190 --> 00:11:24,150
making the inquiry remarkably smooth,

252
00:11:25,190 --> 00:11:26,990
which saved us a lot of time.

253
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:30,110
You were the only other person aware

254
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:32,710
of Chancellor Xu's collusion with Wutuo.

255
00:11:34,110 --> 00:11:35,910
Since the assassins were Wutuo agents,

256
00:11:36,870 --> 00:11:38,710
naturally, we suspected Chancellor Xu.

257
00:11:40,590 --> 00:11:41,910
In Jiyang and Rundu,

258
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,510
you defied Chancellor Xu's orders

259
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:46,710
and defended against Wutuo forces

260
00:11:47,070 --> 00:11:48,110
with us.

261
00:11:49,590 --> 00:11:50,950
As Chancellor Xu's disciple,

262
00:11:51,710 --> 00:11:53,030
why did you

263
00:11:53,630 --> 00:11:54,630
do that?

264
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:58,470
You know well, Commander Xiao,

265
00:11:58,790 --> 00:12:00,910
officials often act against their will.

266
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:04,030
Different stances
dictate different actions.

267
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:05,670
But everything I've done

268
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:07,270
follows the natural course.

269
00:12:07,710 --> 00:12:10,830
I will never
cross the ethical boundaries.

270
00:12:11,990 --> 00:12:12,950
I believe that

271
00:12:13,750 --> 00:12:14,710
you have principles.

272
00:12:15,790 --> 00:12:16,950
But above those principles,

273
00:12:17,470 --> 00:12:18,910
right and wrong exist.

274
00:12:19,350 --> 00:12:20,310
I hope you won't

275
00:12:20,590 --> 00:12:22,630
have to face so many helpless situations

276
00:12:22,990 --> 00:12:23,910
or feel powerless.

277
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:29,990
Thank you
for your kindness and blessings.

278
00:12:34,990 --> 00:12:36,310
I'll take my leave now.

279
00:12:36,910 --> 00:12:37,750
Farewell.

280
00:12:48,910 --> 00:12:50,030
I hope you don't blame me

281
00:12:50,470 --> 00:12:52,390
for not telling you those earlier.

282
00:12:53,830 --> 00:12:54,670
Of course not.

283
00:12:56,110 --> 00:12:56,990
But Commander,

284
00:12:57,550 --> 00:12:59,470
Mr. Chu isn't truly evil.

285
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:02,950
Perhaps, we could work with him one day.

286
00:13:13,590 --> 00:13:15,950
She's just a masked impostor,

287
00:13:16,710 --> 00:13:19,150
hiding behind others' prestige.

288
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:22,310
Yet they praise her false heroism

289
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:24,470
for lifting Rundu's siege.

290
00:13:25,030 --> 00:13:28,270
I am the true General Feihong.

291
00:13:29,550 --> 00:13:31,390
That's me.

292
00:13:40,670 --> 00:13:42,030
My dear sister.

293
00:13:43,470 --> 00:13:46,390
The soul-calming lantern
in Yuhua Temple couldn't suppress you.

294
00:13:47,110 --> 00:13:49,990
The trap in Rundu couldn't kill you.

295
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:53,510
You are truly

296
00:13:53,990 --> 00:13:56,550
relentless as a lingering ghost.

297
00:13:59,950 --> 00:14:00,950
(General He.)

298
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:04,430
Mr. Maningbu sent you a message.

299
00:14:04,710 --> 00:14:07,870
Wutuo sincerely seeks cooperation.

300
00:14:08,270 --> 00:14:10,030
We agreed

301
00:14:10,230 --> 00:14:12,830
to help you kill the seven warriors

302
00:14:13,590 --> 00:14:15,790
in exchange for Rundu.

303
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,390
But

304
00:14:17,590 --> 00:14:20,630
where did that fake
General Feihong come from?

305
00:14:21,110 --> 00:14:24,390
And why was General Fengyun in Rundu?

306
00:14:24,830 --> 00:14:25,910
The Rundu battle

307
00:14:26,390 --> 00:14:28,870
cost Wutuo significant forces.

308
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,510
And in Jiyang,

309
00:14:30,870 --> 00:14:32,750
those two people ruined

310
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:34,670
Wutuo's plan.

311
00:14:35,230 --> 00:14:36,510
Could it be

312
00:14:37,430 --> 00:14:39,510
that Chancellor Xu changed strategies?

313
00:14:40,030 --> 00:14:44,030
Have you reconciled
and colluded with Xiao Jue

314
00:14:44,190 --> 00:14:46,870
to fool Mr. Maningbu

315
00:14:46,990 --> 00:14:48,350
and mock Wutuo?

316
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:53,190
This time,

317
00:14:53,950 --> 00:14:55,750
I was truly outplayed.

318
00:14:58,350 --> 00:14:59,190
However,

319
00:14:59,510 --> 00:15:01,070
I genuinely wish

320
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:02,910
to cooperate with Mr. Maningbu.

321
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:05,830
Please convey

322
00:15:05,990 --> 00:15:10,150
my deepest apologies to Mr. Maningbu.

323
00:15:11,110 --> 00:15:13,830
Since you put it this way,

324
00:15:14,110 --> 00:15:16,310
we naturally believe you.

325
00:15:16,670 --> 00:15:20,430
But Wutuo has suffered huge losses.

326
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:21,510
General He.

327
00:15:21,590 --> 00:15:22,910
When you meet Chancellor Xu,

328
00:15:23,350 --> 00:15:24,910
please tell him

329
00:15:25,470 --> 00:15:28,310
that Wutuo won't
accept such humiliation.

330
00:15:29,030 --> 00:15:33,630
We expect Chancellor Xu
to provide a reasonable explanation.

331
00:15:45,630 --> 00:15:46,470
Chancellor.

332
00:15:46,870 --> 00:15:49,550
His Majesty has allowed Xiao Jue
to return and report

333
00:15:49,950 --> 00:15:51,150
on the Rundu Battle.

334
00:15:51,750 --> 00:15:53,990
He knew I wanted to kill him in Rundu.

335
00:15:54,110 --> 00:15:55,550
Now he's coming back for revenge.

336
00:15:56,190 --> 00:15:58,070
And the Mingshui Battle, Chancellor.

337
00:15:58,590 --> 00:16:00,350
They will never let this go.

338
00:16:00,830 --> 00:16:01,670
Chancellor.

339
00:16:01,950 --> 00:16:02,950
Please help me.

340
00:16:03,910 --> 00:16:05,190
Were you trying

341
00:16:05,950 --> 00:16:08,110
to kill Xiao Jue in the Rundu battle?

342
00:16:12,150 --> 00:16:13,630
At this point,

343
00:16:13,990 --> 00:16:16,190
are you still hiding the truth?

344
00:16:16,990 --> 00:16:21,990
Who is that masked
young general in Rundu?

345
00:16:23,030 --> 00:16:24,230
Can anyone just

346
00:16:24,390 --> 00:16:27,470
impersonate General Feihong at will?

347
00:16:28,510 --> 00:16:29,430
He Rufei.

348
00:16:29,670 --> 00:16:32,710
How dare you keep me in the dark

349
00:16:33,030 --> 00:16:34,270
about this!

350
00:16:35,670 --> 00:16:36,510
I apologize.

351
00:16:37,470 --> 00:16:38,310
Please forgive me.

352
00:16:39,030 --> 00:16:39,870
Chancellor.

353
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:42,310
I wasn't sure
whether my sister was alive.

354
00:16:42,590 --> 00:16:44,670
That's why I used
the Rundu Battle as bait.

355
00:16:44,670 --> 00:16:46,990
I planned to kill her in Rundu
even if she was alive.

356
00:16:47,390 --> 00:16:48,310
But I didn't expect

357
00:16:48,750 --> 00:16:50,390
that she would be so hard to kill.

358
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,510
Hard to kill?

359
00:16:52,070 --> 00:16:54,430
Had you disclosed this earlier,

360
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:57,550
you wouldn't be
kneeling before me in disgrace.

361
00:16:59,710 --> 00:17:00,870
You barely won

362
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:03,070
the Huayuan Battle,

363
00:17:03,190 --> 00:17:04,630
losing seven top warriors.

364
00:17:05,510 --> 00:17:08,869
Someone disguised
as General Feihong in Rundu

365
00:17:09,069 --> 00:17:11,150
to intimidate the Wutuo Army,

366
00:17:11,190 --> 00:17:12,750
while the real General Feihong

367
00:17:12,869 --> 00:17:14,990
failed to provide timely reinforcement.

368
00:17:15,069 --> 00:17:17,390
His Majesty has heard about all this.

369
00:17:19,910 --> 00:17:22,990
Both Huayuan and Rundu battles

370
00:17:23,190 --> 00:17:25,750
bear a striking resemblance
to Mingshui Battle.

371
00:17:25,910 --> 00:17:28,069
People will inevitably draw connections.

372
00:17:28,950 --> 00:17:32,030
Xiao Jue and your sister
will pursue this relentlessly.

373
00:17:32,230 --> 00:17:35,830
His Majesty will also order
a full investigation.

374
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:39,190
They might even reopen
the Mingshui Battle investigation.

375
00:17:42,470 --> 00:17:44,590
He Rufei.

376
00:17:45,030 --> 00:17:46,990
Your concealment

377
00:17:47,230 --> 00:17:49,670
has put us both in deep trouble.

378
00:17:49,950 --> 00:17:52,870
The Wutuo people
won't let us off, either.

379
00:17:55,390 --> 00:17:56,230
That's right.

380
00:17:56,350 --> 00:17:57,190
Chancellor.

381
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:58,710
You're right.

382
00:17:59,350 --> 00:18:00,510
Rest assured, Chancellor.

383
00:18:01,110 --> 00:18:04,030
I will never
keep anything from you again.

384
00:18:05,310 --> 00:18:07,830
Chancellor, please get me out of this.

385
00:18:08,230 --> 00:18:10,590
Chancellor, please save me this time.

386
00:18:10,670 --> 00:18:11,510
Please!

387
00:18:11,510 --> 00:18:12,670
No more secrets ever again.

388
00:18:13,870 --> 00:18:16,750
Good that you've come
to this realization.

389
00:18:17,510 --> 00:18:22,390
Absolute transparency
is the key to our collaboration.

390
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,110
That's enough.

391
00:18:24,390 --> 00:18:25,390
I will find a way

392
00:18:25,990 --> 00:18:27,710
to pacify the Wutuo people.

393
00:18:28,470 --> 00:18:29,510
And I will emphasize

394
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:31,910
your contributions

395
00:18:33,070 --> 00:18:34,430
to His Majesty,

396
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:35,630
while shifting blame

397
00:18:36,270 --> 00:18:38,190
onto the enemies.

398
00:18:38,750 --> 00:18:40,910
As for Xiao Jue and your sister,

399
00:18:41,390 --> 00:18:43,030
if my predictions hold,

400
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:46,070
they're planning to use the scandal

401
00:18:46,110 --> 00:18:47,950
of your family swapping your identities

402
00:18:48,310 --> 00:18:49,270
as leverage.

403
00:18:49,950 --> 00:18:52,310
Now that they had finally
found a chance,

404
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:54,510
they requested permission to return.

405
00:18:54,670 --> 00:18:57,190
They'll use you to get what they want.

406
00:19:01,990 --> 00:19:02,830
We can't

407
00:19:04,070 --> 00:19:06,030
let them come back alive.

408
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:08,390
Commander Li.

409
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:09,750
Open this letter

410
00:19:10,150 --> 00:19:11,350
after we leave.

411
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:20,110
General Fengyun, Attendant Wu'an,
General Yan. Safe travels.

412
00:19:20,550 --> 00:19:21,430
I'll drink with you

413
00:19:21,630 --> 00:19:22,670
in the capital

414
00:19:23,270 --> 00:19:24,630
after the Mid-Autumn Festival.

415
00:19:29,430 --> 00:19:30,270
Wait.

416
00:19:36,110 --> 00:19:37,710
Attendant Wu'an, a moment please.

417
00:19:42,910 --> 00:19:43,750
Attendant Wu'an.

418
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:45,030
We will never

419
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:47,070
forget what you said to us.

420
00:19:47,550 --> 00:19:48,910
We'll do our best to live on.

421
00:19:49,830 --> 00:19:52,110
We've set up a textile workshop,

422
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:54,030
making a living on our own.

423
00:19:55,270 --> 00:19:57,110
Though we can't fight enemies as you do,

424
00:19:57,430 --> 00:19:59,510
we can make minor contributions.

425
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:02,550
We'll bring Rundu's
brocade weaving to greater heights

426
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:03,950
across the entire Wei.

427
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:06,270
No job is superior or inferior.

428
00:20:06,790 --> 00:20:08,190
Everything improves

429
00:20:08,390 --> 00:20:09,950
through gradual efforts.

430
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:11,630
Change will come

431
00:20:11,870 --> 00:20:13,070
as long as you take action.

432
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,590
Then I'll wait

433
00:20:14,870 --> 00:20:16,270
to see Rundu's brocade

434
00:20:16,430 --> 00:20:17,470
known throughout Wei.

435
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:19,070
Alright.

436
00:20:19,670 --> 00:20:21,310
You are indeed popular.

437
00:20:21,390 --> 00:20:23,230
But I don't envy you at all.

438
00:20:24,150 --> 00:20:24,990
I'm leaving, He Yan.

439
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,110
My wife is waiting at home.

440
00:20:27,670 --> 00:20:28,590
Got it.

441
00:20:29,150 --> 00:20:30,430
Only you have a wife, huh?

442
00:20:31,510 --> 00:20:33,190
Attendant Wu'an inspires people

443
00:20:33,430 --> 00:20:35,350
with the resilience he possesses.

444
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:40,110
Many people may
show consideration for others,

445
00:20:40,390 --> 00:20:41,230
but

446
00:20:41,430 --> 00:20:42,670
those who would

447
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:44,070
sacrifice themselves

448
00:20:45,110 --> 00:20:47,030
for other people at critical moments

449
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:49,070
are exceedingly rare.

450
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:51,030
(He truly resembles)

451
00:20:51,030 --> 00:20:52,190
(General Feihong back then.)

452
00:21:05,030 --> 00:21:05,870
Your Majesty.

453
00:21:06,590 --> 00:21:07,670
During the Rundu Battle,

454
00:21:07,910 --> 00:21:10,590
He Yan led the locals
in unwavering defense,

455
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:13,230
while Xiao Jue
offered timely reinforcements.

456
00:21:13,510 --> 00:21:14,830
Together, they defended Rundu

457
00:21:15,110 --> 00:21:16,230
against the Wutuo army.

458
00:21:16,430 --> 00:21:17,830
It was a great contribution.

459
00:21:18,390 --> 00:21:20,110
I'm well aware of Xiao Jue's

460
00:21:20,430 --> 00:21:21,350
military prowess.

461
00:21:21,910 --> 00:21:22,910
But He Yan

462
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:24,750
used to be relatively unknown,

463
00:21:25,030 --> 00:21:27,710
but recently
he's been showing his talent.

464
00:21:28,670 --> 00:21:29,750
He's a real talent.

465
00:21:30,470 --> 00:21:31,310
Your Majesty.

466
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:32,430
In my humble opinion,

467
00:21:32,950 --> 00:21:33,790
Attendant Wu'an

468
00:21:34,190 --> 00:21:35,310
has the potential

469
00:21:35,590 --> 00:21:36,430
to be a general.

470
00:21:36,950 --> 00:21:37,990
Most remarkably,

471
00:21:38,190 --> 00:21:40,270
his heart beats with patriotic bravery

472
00:21:40,430 --> 00:21:41,910
and unyielding resolve.

473
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:45,830
On the contrary, He Rufei,

474
00:21:46,630 --> 00:21:48,150
once considered capable,

475
00:21:48,710 --> 00:21:51,110
has proven utterly incompetent.

476
00:21:51,710 --> 00:21:52,590
He lost

477
00:21:53,230 --> 00:21:55,710
seven of our top warriors in Huayuan.

478
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:58,350
Your Majesty.

479
00:21:58,710 --> 00:21:59,550
The Huayuan Battle

480
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:01,270
was a costly victory.

481
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:03,590
But our enemies are well-equipped,

482
00:22:03,870 --> 00:22:05,390
and they far outnumber us.

483
00:22:06,070 --> 00:22:06,910
I believe

484
00:22:07,270 --> 00:22:08,110
that General He

485
00:22:09,230 --> 00:22:10,750
may have done his utmost.

486
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:13,950
"May have?"

487
00:22:20,710 --> 00:22:21,550
Enough.

488
00:22:21,950 --> 00:22:22,790
Forget about them.

489
00:22:23,790 --> 00:22:24,630
Mr. Chu,

490
00:22:25,470 --> 00:22:27,550
you put yourself at risk
and defended Rundu.

491
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:29,350
It deserves recognition.

492
00:22:29,990 --> 00:22:31,150
Why didn't you bring it up?

493
00:22:31,670 --> 00:22:33,750
My minor contributions
aren't worth mentioning.

494
00:22:37,150 --> 00:22:39,310
Last time, you asked for rewards.

495
00:22:39,710 --> 00:22:42,110
Why are you declining them now?

496
00:22:42,670 --> 00:22:44,350
Your previous rewards

497
00:22:44,550 --> 00:22:46,710
allowed me to take action in Rundu.

498
00:22:47,150 --> 00:22:49,110
I merely wanted to serve Your Majesty.

499
00:22:49,390 --> 00:22:51,070
Thus, I need no further rewards.

500
00:22:52,310 --> 00:22:54,470
Xiao Jue and Chancellor Xu
don't get along.

501
00:22:54,910 --> 00:22:56,990
As Chancellor Xu's prized disciple,

502
00:22:57,590 --> 00:22:59,230
it's commendable that you're speaking

503
00:23:00,110 --> 00:23:01,270
in favor of Xiao Jue.

504
00:23:02,950 --> 00:23:05,430
Ministers may differ politically,

505
00:23:06,110 --> 00:23:07,950
but we stand united in loyalty

506
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:10,070
to Your Majesty.

507
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:14,390
Pass on my decree.

508
00:23:15,670 --> 00:23:17,150
Director Chu Zhao

509
00:23:17,990 --> 00:23:19,030
of the Ministry of War

510
00:23:19,470 --> 00:23:22,630
is a true pillar of Wei,
having shouldered my burdens repeatedly.

511
00:23:23,070 --> 00:23:23,910
I hereby

512
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:25,710
appoint Chu Zhao

513
00:23:26,630 --> 00:23:28,870
as Fourth-Rank Vice Minister of War.

514
00:23:29,150 --> 00:23:30,110
Yes, Your Majesty.

515
00:23:33,750 --> 00:23:35,990
I humbly thank Your Majesty.

516
00:23:49,510 --> 00:23:52,470
Master, I went to Rundu on my own

517
00:23:52,750 --> 00:23:54,950
against your instructions.
Please forgive me.

518
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:09,070
His Majesty thinks highly of you
and has given you

519
00:24:09,630 --> 00:24:11,510
another promotion.

520
00:24:13,350 --> 00:24:15,190
You don't need to apologize.

521
00:24:19,590 --> 00:24:20,470
You flatter me.

522
00:24:21,030 --> 00:24:21,870
I'm ashamed.

523
00:24:22,310 --> 00:24:26,230
You've risen in such a short time,

524
00:24:26,830 --> 00:24:31,190
soon to become
His Majesty's right-hand man

525
00:24:31,270 --> 00:24:33,550
and a pillar of Wei.

526
00:24:34,910 --> 00:24:35,910
You are truly

527
00:24:36,630 --> 00:24:38,910
my most accomplished disciple.

528
00:24:40,470 --> 00:24:41,710
I had no choice.

529
00:24:42,350 --> 00:24:43,870
The circumstances forced my hand.

530
00:24:49,270 --> 00:24:50,750
Xiao Jue and He Yan

531
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:53,350
are about to return for rewards.

532
00:24:53,670 --> 00:24:55,910
Is this what you mean by "no choice"?

533
00:24:58,190 --> 00:24:59,950
They kept distinguishing themselves.

534
00:25:00,350 --> 00:25:01,710
I grew anxious, thinking

535
00:25:01,910 --> 00:25:03,430
that I couldn't just let them be.

536
00:25:03,790 --> 00:25:06,030
So I rushed to Rundu
without seeking permission.

537
00:25:11,470 --> 00:25:12,910
The entire court knows

538
00:25:13,310 --> 00:25:14,390
that I'm your disciple.

539
00:25:15,230 --> 00:25:17,030
His Majesty may have promoted me,

540
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:18,430
but in reality,

541
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:20,310
he was honoring you.

542
00:25:21,430 --> 00:25:22,270
Moreover,

543
00:25:22,670 --> 00:25:23,510
the higher I climb,

544
00:25:24,230 --> 00:25:26,310
the more useful I can be to you.

545
00:25:32,550 --> 00:25:35,390
Since you wish to share my burdens,

546
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:37,470
you should know

547
00:25:37,910 --> 00:25:41,070
my greatest concern at hand

548
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:43,070
is He Rufei.

549
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:46,270
You just returned from court.

550
00:25:46,710 --> 00:25:47,910
What is His Majesty

551
00:25:48,830 --> 00:25:50,470
thinking about him?

552
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,550
His Majesty is indeed displeased

553
00:25:52,670 --> 00:25:55,150
with He Rufei's performance at Huayuan.

554
00:25:55,470 --> 00:25:57,430
But I've pleaded his case

555
00:25:57,510 --> 00:25:58,430
by explaining that

556
00:25:59,110 --> 00:26:00,670
our enemies outnumbered us,

557
00:26:01,270 --> 00:26:03,870
and He Rufei may have done his best.

558
00:26:07,630 --> 00:26:09,070
Do you truly believe that?

559
00:26:12,990 --> 00:26:13,830
In my opinion,

560
00:26:14,230 --> 00:26:16,230
it's fishy that the seven warriors

561
00:26:16,470 --> 00:26:17,750
died in an ambush.

562
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,830
But after the Rundu Battle,

563
00:26:20,230 --> 00:26:21,350
I figured it all out.

564
00:26:22,150 --> 00:26:24,910
The Rundu Battle was a trap
He Rufei set for Xiao Jue.

565
00:26:25,630 --> 00:26:26,990
He Rufei needed

566
00:26:27,350 --> 00:26:30,390
huge losses in Huayuan
to avoid reinforcing Rundu.

567
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:31,990
That's how the trap

568
00:26:32,590 --> 00:26:33,430
would work.

569
00:26:34,390 --> 00:26:35,230
However,

570
00:26:35,750 --> 00:26:37,990
Xiao Jue summoned Yan He

571
00:26:38,310 --> 00:26:39,550
and defended Rundu.

572
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,430
He Rufei

573
00:26:41,870 --> 00:26:43,670
miscalculated and lost.

574
00:26:46,390 --> 00:26:47,230
Alright.

575
00:26:47,790 --> 00:26:48,830
It seems

576
00:26:49,390 --> 00:26:50,910
that you have indeed

577
00:26:51,190 --> 00:26:52,910
exerted great effort.

578
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,230
I heard Zilan came.

579
00:26:58,790 --> 00:26:59,750
I knew he'd be here.

580
00:27:01,110 --> 00:27:02,430
Why haven't you come to see me?

581
00:27:03,350 --> 00:27:04,190
Alright.

582
00:27:05,310 --> 00:27:06,790
My business here concludes.

583
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,510
Pingting keeps mentioning you.

584
00:27:10,030 --> 00:27:10,870
Keep her company.

585
00:27:12,190 --> 00:27:14,710
You must be busy, Master.
Don't let me disrupt you.

586
00:27:19,710 --> 00:27:20,550
Sorry.

587
00:27:20,950 --> 00:27:21,830
I have things

588
00:27:21,990 --> 00:27:22,990
to attend to today.

589
00:27:24,110 --> 00:27:25,510
What about tomorrow?

590
00:27:25,670 --> 00:27:26,750
I have other jobs.

591
00:27:27,150 --> 00:27:27,990
The day after?

592
00:27:29,150 --> 00:27:30,110
And beyond?

593
00:27:35,540 --> 00:27:37,790
(Chu Mansion)

594
00:27:38,230 --> 00:27:40,630
- Is the banquet ready?
- All set.

595
00:27:40,630 --> 00:27:42,550
Don't make any mistakes.

596
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:43,390
Rest assured.

597
00:27:43,390 --> 00:27:44,350
It's an important day.

598
00:27:44,870 --> 00:27:47,270
- We must please him.
- Mr. Chu.

599
00:27:47,270 --> 00:27:48,270
Rest assured.

600
00:27:55,910 --> 00:27:56,750
Zilan.

601
00:27:56,750 --> 00:27:57,950
You're finally back.

602
00:27:58,430 --> 00:28:00,030
We've been waiting

603
00:28:00,190 --> 00:28:01,670
