604
00:28:02,270 --> 00:28:03,110
That's right.

605
00:28:03,510 --> 00:28:04,630
Sorry I've kept you waiting.

606
00:28:05,230 --> 00:28:06,310
I went to report

607
00:28:06,470 --> 00:28:07,510
to His Majesty first

608
00:28:08,470 --> 00:28:10,070
and paid respects to my master.

609
00:28:10,950 --> 00:28:11,790
That's why I'm late.

610
00:28:12,150 --> 00:28:12,990
It's alright.

611
00:28:13,950 --> 00:28:14,790
No problem.

612
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:17,670
His Majesty thinks highly of you.

613
00:28:18,150 --> 00:28:20,470
Official duties take precedence.

614
00:28:24,350 --> 00:28:25,190
Yeah.

615
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:26,550
Focus on your work.

616
00:28:27,110 --> 00:28:29,510
Leave trivial matters
to your uncle and me.

617
00:28:30,190 --> 00:28:31,270
Let me know

618
00:28:31,550 --> 00:28:32,750
if you need anything.

619
00:28:33,190 --> 00:28:35,710
We'll arrange everything.

620
00:28:35,950 --> 00:28:37,070
Actually, there is

621
00:28:37,230 --> 00:28:38,070
nothing

622
00:28:38,070 --> 00:28:38,910
I need.

623
00:28:39,510 --> 00:28:40,950
But one thing has weighed on me

624
00:28:41,790 --> 00:28:42,710
for years.

625
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:50,230
What's troubling you?

626
00:28:51,070 --> 00:28:52,070
Tell us.

627
00:28:54,310 --> 00:28:55,750
Don't you want your

628
00:28:55,830 --> 00:28:56,750
scandalous mother,

629
00:28:57,190 --> 00:28:58,470
who gave birth unwed,

630
00:28:58,670 --> 00:29:00,030
to enter the Chu ancestral hall?

631
00:29:00,670 --> 00:29:02,350
Then rise

632
00:29:02,630 --> 00:29:04,030
to prominence quickly.

633
00:29:06,830 --> 00:29:08,070
My deepest wish

634
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:10,350
is only for my mother

635
00:29:11,790 --> 00:29:13,110
to find eternal peace.

636
00:29:24,110 --> 00:29:25,590
So, you still don't think

637
00:29:25,870 --> 00:29:26,710
my mother...

638
00:29:26,710 --> 00:29:27,550
You got us wrong.

639
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:28,550
You got us wrong.

640
00:29:30,230 --> 00:29:31,790
My sister was virtuous and dignified.

641
00:29:31,950 --> 00:29:33,790
She deserves to be enshrined

642
00:29:33,990 --> 00:29:35,510
in the ancestral hall.

643
00:29:39,190 --> 00:29:40,030
Zilan,

644
00:29:41,390 --> 00:29:42,630
your mother...

645
00:29:45,830 --> 00:29:47,150
Your aunt was

646
00:29:47,550 --> 00:29:49,470
not good with words.

647
00:29:50,110 --> 00:29:51,590
Please don't take

648
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:54,030
her gibberish to heart.

649
00:29:56,230 --> 00:29:58,430
I was stupid and often misspoke.

650
00:29:58,990 --> 00:30:00,630
P-Please forgive me.

651
00:30:03,470 --> 00:30:04,310
In that case,

652
00:30:05,710 --> 00:30:06,750
I truly appreciate it.

653
00:30:07,430 --> 00:30:08,270
Our pleasure.

654
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:09,550
Our pleasure.

655
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,850
(Late Mother, Chu Mingfang)

656
00:30:23,430 --> 00:30:24,270
Mother,

657
00:30:25,150 --> 00:30:26,350
I'm bringing you home.

658
00:30:28,270 --> 00:30:29,390
From now on,

659
00:30:30,150 --> 00:30:31,630
