660
00:30:32,830 --> 00:30:33,670
ever again.

661
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:42,190
My dear, poor sister.

662
00:30:43,030 --> 00:30:44,830
I've wronged you.

663
00:30:44,990 --> 00:30:45,950
But rest assured.

664
00:30:46,190 --> 00:30:47,070
From now on,

665
00:30:47,150 --> 00:30:48,110
I won't let you

666
00:30:48,230 --> 00:30:49,910
suffer any humiliation again.

667
00:30:59,190 --> 00:31:01,270
You have acknowledged your mistakes.

668
00:31:03,750 --> 00:31:05,150
Mother's spirit must find this

669
00:31:06,150 --> 00:31:07,190
