677
00:31:25,190 --> 00:31:26,070
Should we come often?

678
00:31:26,470 --> 00:31:27,310
Silence.

679
00:31:29,990 --> 00:31:30,830
Absolutely.

680
00:31:31,510 --> 00:31:32,350
Absolutely.

681
00:31:33,630 --> 00:31:34,630
We will.

682
00:31:42,990 --> 00:31:45,790
(Late Mother, Chu Mingfang)
(I'll bring her to meet you.)

683
00:31:47,510 --> 00:31:48,350
(Mother.)

684
00:31:48,990 --> 00:31:50,430
(I have found that light.)

685
00:31:51,750 --> 00:31:53,910
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

686
00:31:54,010 --> 00:31:57,930
